</p>
<p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center " id="SE-1708ffa0-b780-40cd-8299-7e2a73065892" style="text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff">
	<span class="se-fs- se-ff-   " id="SE-76f4edb8-72af-4fa1-a228-a9b7f2d423e7" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline">그냥 코드 업로드해놓은 것이 전부가 아니라,</span>
</p>
<p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center " id="SE-bdf310de-3a9e-4f2d-b7ed-b31885b34072" style="text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff">
	<span class="se-fs- se-ff-   " id="SE-ffa6d435-00fa-42de-95a8-c7ec9e7f4a11" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline">각 chapter 별로 branch를 만들어 놔서</span>
</p>
<p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center " id="SE-6697db34-db68-48e3-9ee8-30cf6a0143cc" style="text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff">
	<span class="se-fs- se-ff-   " id="SE-cc7d4603-b375-4980-898f-7631bc41d43b" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline">새로운 chapter를 시작할 때 그에 맞는 branch를 다시 당겨오면 되기 때문에</span>
</p>
<p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center " id="SE-51a1128c-93da-40a2-b7d8-e14001e801e7" style="text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff">
	<span class="se-fs- se-ff-   " id="SE-264b249b-9f46-49bf-a52c-7d70fe404fed" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline">도서의 코드를 못 따라갈 일이 없습니다.</span>
</p>
<p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center " id="SE-d03f65da-3174-4638-87a5-033036e094e5" style="text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff">
	<span class="se-fs- se-ff-   " id="SE-f63f5321-07e6-488b-bbd7-b025417cf5fa" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline">​</span>
</p>
<p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center " id="SE-4c84bd70-b5c4-4e83-b194-76b228f67b34" style="text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff">
	<span class="se-fs- se-ff-   " id="SE-2e023362-4a5d-4d13-af22-36a80801a556" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline">시중의 몇몇 책들 중에는 분명 책에 적힌대로 따라 했는데</span>
</p>
<p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center " id="SE-586d2bfd-924f-4a8e-9869-f34834d24ece" style="text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff">
	<span class="se-fs- se-ff-   " id="SE-7097bb23-236c-4036-8110-e77b04f2356e" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline">잘 안되서 삽질하는 경우가 있잖아요?</span>
</p>
<p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center " id="SE-5d84cad6-dd50-4f2f-a817-0c52423a9ce3" style="text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff">
	<span class="se-fs- se-ff-   " id="SE-a06c05d9-7785-4d7c-a871-aea85de7fe61" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline">이 책을 보면서 그럴 일은 없을 겁니다.</span>
</p>
<p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center " id="SE-9c33c4f3-5f6d-4c2a-b00c-ef0e3b237806" style="text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff">
	<span class="se-fs- se-ff-   " id="SE-5744e719-20f7-4a4c-860a-e3033ad80a62" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline">뭔가 이상하면, 그냥 branch를 당겨오세요 ㅎㅎ</span>
</p>
<p class="se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center " id="SE-14fa1a72-a101-49db-a348-746a2cfbda38" style="text-align: left; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-variant-east-asian: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 0px; line-height: 1.8; font-family: se-nanumgothic, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff">
